  <entry>
    <title>Hexo[Next] @ Set transparency and margins</title>
    <url>/2020/09/01/2020-09-01-Hexo-Next-Set-transparency-and-margins/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>Go to the custom style file:</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd ./site_folder/source/_data/styles.styl | vi</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>



<p>Add the code as below:</p>
<a id="more"></a>

<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="string">//1_The</span> <span class="string">menu</span> <span class="string">bar</span> <span class="string">tranparency</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">.header-inner</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">rgba(255</span>,<span class="number">255</span>,<span class="number">255</span>,<span class="number">0.7</span><span class="string">);</span> <span class="string">//from</span> <span class="number">0</span><span class="number">-1</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">//2_Avatar</span> <span class="string">info</span> <span class="string">bar</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">.sidebar</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">opacity:</span> <span class="number">0.85</span><span class="string">;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">//3_local-search</span> <span class="string">box</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">.popup</span> &#123;</span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">opacity:</span> <span class="number">0.9</span><span class="string">;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">//4_post</span> <span class="string">tranparency</span> <span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">middle</span> <span class="string">body</span> <span class="string">tranparency</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="string">.main-inner</span> &#123; </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">margin-top:</span> <span class="string">20px;</span>  <span class="string">//Margin</span> <span class="string">from</span> <span class="string">the</span> <span class="string">top</span> <span class="string">of</span> <span class="string">the</span> <span class="string">page</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">padding:</span> <span class="string">20px</span> <span class="string">40px</span> <span class="string">20px</span> <span class="string">40px;</span> <span class="string">//</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">margin</span> <span class="string">for</span> <span class="string">up</span>,<span class="string">right</span>,<span class="string">down</span>,<span class="string">and</span> <span class="string">left.</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">background:</span> <span class="string">none;</span> <span class="string">//The</span> <span class="string">page</span> <span class="string">margin</span> <span class="string">color</span>, <span class="comment">#fff [white] is default. //&quot;none&quot; is transparent</span></span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">opacity:</span> <span class="number">0.90</span><span class="string">;</span>     </span><br><span class="line">    <span class="attr">min-height:</span> <span class="string">500px;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#125;</span><br><span class="line"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>You can now customize all the transparency of your site and margins.</p>
<p>Good luck！</p>
]]></content>
