  <entry>
    <title>Hexo[Next] @ add Comment System in your site</title>
    <url>/2020/09/01/2020-09-01-Hexo-Next-add-Comment-system-in-your-site/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>First, go to <code>Disqus</code>website, to sign up for an account,</p>
<p>Keep in mind your <code>shortname</code>.</p>
<p>Go to :</p>
<figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cd .&#x2F;site_folder&#x2F;themes&#x2F;next&#x2F;_config.yml</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<a id="more"></a>

<p>Locate to the code block as below:</p>
<figure class="highlight yml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="comment"># Disqus</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="attr">disqus:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">enable:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">shortname:</span> <span class="string">yl-jia</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">count:</span> <span class="literal">true</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>Add your own “shortname”, and enable “true”, then the Comment system is working.</p>
]]></content>
